{"tid":48371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"家姐迷信風水，兼上網識男人","createTime":"2016-12-21T04:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T05:21:38.000Z","uid":31875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f6bceb416278d73b82f77ae223816296b22611","tid":48371,"uid":31875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"家姐以前細個個時成日話d男人有乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，成日舉例話邊個老公/男友點點點衰，例如失業，沉迷賭博等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，完全無拍拖既念頭。<br />\n<br />\n後來信左教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一放工就去搞宗教活動，個陣我心諗佢變左全職教徒，工作似變左副業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n信左幾年教，佢而家無咁熱衷，最近聽人講話有師傅算命好準喎，就走去算命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n算命內容大約係佢會行桃花運，2年後會結婚，結婚對象係中產，雖然而家有好多桃花，但過幾年仲多桃花，到時果個會仲有錢。<br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢而家已經3x歲，過幾年已經4字頭，有乜可能40歲既桃花仲多過30歲?我唔好意思同佢講，費時以為我串佢老。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽完算命先生9 up後，佢開始上網識人，好彩仲未比人騙財色，試過識左個一出黎就要求上床，佢唔肯，個男人見無肉食就消失。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔寫咁詳細了，費時比佢發現。<br />\n家姐而家年紀唔細，但就嫌三嫌四，嫌a君樣衰，嫌b君矮，仲迷信到以為過幾年會識到個更有錢，我都唔知點勸佢降低要求，屋企人都想佢有個伴(要求係有正當職業)，老左唔洗自己一個孤伶伶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea247d68713c122fd9437dd37865304350452cc","tid":48371,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8678a54913b4e3e39666149075287a9f3c97fed0","tid":48371,"uid":39370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"係佢自己問題 幫唔到 佢唔會聽得入耳<br />\n見佢成日轉思想 都係個無主見嘅人<br />\n真係祝佢好運🍀"},{"pid":"abc8f191aede50e8e1df2405fb4153502020e315","tid":48371,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"應該遲d會信性交轉運"},{"pid":"70eb7cf8e70aefb719748850957c7c85ed76391c","tid":48371,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3593f5b3cf88e361690427810af8b1f65d35a5","tid":48371,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ee416e11799be32f84dba454b7649a0b960ef0","tid":48371,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"岑晉晴"},{"pid":"f20f7ee1ed240cd6be64f74073674615bd0dec7a","tid":48371,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係佢自己問題 幫唔到 佢唔會聽得入耳<br />\n見佢成日轉思想 都係個無主見嘅人<br />\n真係祝佢好運🍀</blockquote><br />\n咁就易搞 諗計比樓主摧毀佢信念放棄呢個諗法"}]}